{"title_page": "Fernando Matos", "text_new": "{{short description|Portuguese judoka}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Fernando Matos\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Portuguese\n| sport          = [[Judo]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1941|4|1|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Fernando Matos''' (born 1 April 1941) is a Portuguese [[judo]]ka. He competed in the [[Judo at the 1964 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 80 kg|men's middleweight event]] at the [[1964 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ma/fernando-matos-1.html |title=Fernando Matos Olympic Results |accessdate=7 May 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Matos, Fernando}}\n[[Category:1941 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Portuguese male judoka]]\n[[Category:Olympic judoka of Portugal]]\n[[Category:Judoka at the 1964 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n{{Portugal-judo-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Fernando Matos\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Portuguese\n| sport          = [[Judo]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1941|4|1|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Fernando Matos''' (born 1 April 1941) is a Portuguese [[judo]]ka. He competed in the [[Judo at the 1964 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 80 kg|men's middleweight event]] at the [[1964 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ma/fernando-matos-1.html |title=Fernando Matos Olympic Results |accessdate=7 May 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n