{"title_page": "Jo\u00e3o Neves", "text_new": "{{short description|Portuguese judoka}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Jo\u00e3o Neves\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Portuguese\n| sport          = [[Judo]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1963|11|6|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Jo\u00e3o Neves''' (born 6 November 1963) is a Portuguese [[judo]]ka. He competed in the [[Judo at the 1984 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 60 kg|men's extra-lightweight event]] at the [[1984 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ne/joao-neves-1.html |title=Jo\u00e3o Neves Olympic Results |accessdate=20 May 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Neves, Joao}}\n[[Category:1963 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Portuguese male judoka]]\n[[Category:Olympic judoka of Portugal]]\n[[Category:Judoka at the 1984 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n{{Portugal-judo-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2018}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Jo\u00e3o Neves\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Portuguese\n| sport          = [[Judo]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1963|11|6|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Jo\u00e3o Neves''' (born 6 November 1963) is a Portuguese [[judo]]ka. He competed in the [[Judo at the 1984 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's 60 kg|men's extra-lightweight event]] at the [[1984 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ne/joao-neves-1.html |title=Jo\u00e3o Neves Olympic Results |accessdate=20 May 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authorit