 Cavalry Regiment, 5th Squadron</center>\nFile:91CavRegt1SquadFlash.jpg|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd Airborne Brigade's]] [[91st Cavalry Regiment]], 1st Squadron</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Civil affairs|Civil Affairs]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:95CivilAffairsBdeFlash.jpg|<center>[[95th Civil Affairs Brigade|95th Civil Affairs Brigade (Special Operations)]]</center>\nFile:US Army 91st Civil Affairs Battalion Flash.png|<center>95th Civil Affairs Brigade's 91st Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 92nd Civil Affairs Battalion Flash.png|<center>95th Civil Affairs Brigade's 92nd Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:96 Civil Affairs Battalion Flash.png|<center>95th Civil Affairs Brigade's [[96th Civil Affairs Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 97th Civil Affairs Battalion Flash.png|<center>95th Civil Affairs Brigade's [[97th Civil Affairs Battalion (Airborne)|97th Civil Affairs Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 98th Civil Affairs Battalion Flash.png|<center>95th Civil Affairs Brigade's [[98th Civil Affairs Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 404th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>304th Civil Affairs Brigade's 404th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 478th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>350th Civil Affairs Command's 478th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 416th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>358th Civil Affairs Brigade's 416th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 426th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>358th Civil Affairs Brigade's 426th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 360th Civil Affairs Bde Flash.png|<center>[[360th Civil Affairs Brigade (United States)|360th Civil Affairs Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 412th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>360th Civil Affairs Brigade's 412th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 450th Civil Affairs Bn Flash.png|<center>360th Civil Affairs Brigade's 450th Civil Affairs Battalion</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[United States Army Corps of Engineers|Engineer]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 27th Engineer Bn Flash.png|<center>[[20th Engineer Brigade (United States)|20th Engineer Brigade's]] (ENG BDE) [[27th Engineer Battalion (United States)|27th Engineer Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 57th Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>20th ENG BDE, 27th Engineer Battalion's 57th Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 161st Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>20th ENG BDE, 27th Engineer Battalion's 161st Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 6th Bde Eng Bn Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry Division]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team's]] (IBCT) 6th Engineer Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 127th Bde Engineer BN Flash.png|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division]] (ABN DIV), 1st IBCT's 127th Engineer Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 37th Eng BN Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT's [[37th Engineer Battalion (United States)|37th Engineer Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 738th Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 2nd IBCT, 37th Engineer Battalion's 738th Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 307th Bde Eng BN Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT's 307th Engineer Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 919th Engineer Co Flash.png|<center>82nd ABN DIV, 3rd IBCT, 307th Engineer Battalion's 919th Engineer Company</center>\nFile:US Army 54th Brigade Engineer Battalion Flash.png|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd Airborne Brigade]] [[Special Troops Battalion, 173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team (United States)|54th Engineer Battalion]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Field Artillery Branch (United States)|Field Artillery]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army 2nd Bn-377th Arty Reg Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry Division]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team's]], [[377th Field Artillery Regiment]], 2nd Battalion</center>\nFile:82nd Airborne Division Artillery Beret Flash.svg|<center>[[82nd Airborne Division Artillery]] (ABN DIV ARTY)</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV ARTY's [[319th Field Artillery Regiment]], [[1st Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|1st Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV ARTY's 319th Field Artillery Regiment, [[2nd Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|2nd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 3rd BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>82nd ABN DIV ARTY's 319th Field Artillery Regiment, [[3rd Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|3rd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 4th BN-319th Field Arty Reg Flash.svg|<center>[[173rd Airborne Brigade Combat Team|173rd Airborne Brigade's]] 319th Field Artillery Regiment, [[4th Battalion, 319th Field Artillery Regiment|4th Battalion]]</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Infantry Branch (United States)|Infantry]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:75thrangerflash.svg|<center>[[United States Army Special Operations Command|US Army Special Operations Command]]'s (USASOC) [[75th Ranger Regiment (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment]] and [[Special Troops Battalion]]</center>\nFile:1 Bn 75 Ranger Regiment Beret Flash.svg|<center>USASOC's [[1st Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 1st Battalion]]</center>\nFile:Image5435.gif|<center>USASOC's [[2nd Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 2nd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:Image5436.gif|<center>USASOC's [[3rd Ranger Battalion (United States)|75th Ranger Regiment, 3rd Battalion]]</center>\nFile:US Army 4th Bde-25th ID Flash.png|<center>[[25th Infantry Division (United States)|25th Infantry (INF) Division's (DIV)]], [[4th Brigade Combat Team (Airborne), 25th Infantry Division|4th Infantry Brigade Combat Team]] (IBCT)</center>\nFile:US Army 1st Bn-501st Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>25th INF DIV, 4th IBCT's [[501st Infantry Regiment (United States)|501st Infantry R